videos.description: Trayce Jackson-Davis muscles to the paint and spins for the Indiana dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jackson-Davis spins past defender for Indiana dunk) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jackson-Davis spins past defender for Indiana dunk

videos.description: Minnesota's Daniel Oturu elevates for a dunk, but Indiana's Jerome Hunter has other plans and gets the clean rejection.

videos.headline: Hunter meets Oturu at the rim for impressive block

videos.description: Indiana's Trayce Jackson-Davis puts up a mid-range jumper as the shot clock expires and sinks it.
videos.headline: Jackson-Davis beats shot-clock buzzer
